    "text_content": "#### WHO  \nWorld Health Organization\nThe World Health Organization would like to thank all the\ncontributors external collaborators, reviewers and WHO staff\nwhose dedication, support and expertise over many years\nhave made possible this latest edition of the WHO PEN.",
